At the edge of the Solar System, a huge form blocks the light of the 
distant stars. Well before Pluto's orbit, a big, round planet hovers. 
Its existence will never be known by the inhabitants of its system, 
however.

Hatred, greed, power. Three words. They were embodied by a 
gargantuesque mechanical being named Unicron.

The planet never knew what hit it. Huge claws dug in its crust as 
Unicron grasped it and started devouring it. Mountains were shattered 
in a matter of minutes and the vibrant core at its heart was 
extinguished.

Unicron was not happy. He sent a single message to his minions...

Unicron: FIND THE MATRIX!
